76561198327901000,Not Recommended,657740,34710848,Posted: 3 September,all,Ghostfriendly,"This is a very short and simple tower defence game which its most favourable reviewers couldn't call more than a quiet way to kill an hour or so. Alas, when the game has so little challenge that all enemies were simply being mowed down at spawn point for half that time, I can't even say that.Levels 7-10 need much tougher new enemies, the towers need to be weaker, shorter ranged, and trade range for speed or firing rate for damage more between different types. It would help this if range/damage/speed were individually upgraded rather than upgraded together, or if some non-specialised stats (eg firing rate for snipers) couldn't be upgraded. Gameplay would be much more thoughful if towers had less difference in price (the upgrade system strengthens towers throughout the game already) and more difference in specialised ability. Graphics and ideas for towers/enemies are rather good, but the gameplay just needs more work."
